Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Whether looking for the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,latest TV show to watch or the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,best place to grab lunch, you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,rely on the people around you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for recommendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By offering the ability to share
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,on Your App, you can empower
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,your users to give contextual
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,recommendations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are some important
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,things to consider before you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,offer the ability to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,First is the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In Your App, what will you want
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your user to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an image or a video, or
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe even an experience that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,they've had in Your App?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in Your App is the best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,place to offer the ability to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,share?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you share from a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,screen, is it contextual?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the user know exactly what
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,will be passed to the recipient?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Timing is another important
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,aspect to building a great
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be, when a user is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,completely connected to the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,content they are wanting to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,share; and at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,think, "My friend Kate would
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,love this."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The developers of Crossy Road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,have a great implementation that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,has narrowed all three of these
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They started with an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's quite common to share
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,your progress in a game, but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,losing in Crossy Road is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,actually quite comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They quickly realized that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,people are going to want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,share that moment and created a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,photograph representation and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,previewed it, ready for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing, content and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,placement were all great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the user of Your
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,App.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When are they most emotionally
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,attached to the experience and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,going to want to share it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Another important aspect of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing is placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense for a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing button in a list view
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,here; but on a detail view, it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As I find a session I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,interested in, I might think of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,someone else that could be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,interested and can very quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you offer the ability to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,share in Your App is with an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,action button.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the universal control
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,used by all apps to access
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A great place for an action
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,button in a detail view like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,this is in the title bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps communicate to the user
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can share all the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,information in this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,On tapping that button, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,call a UIActivityViewController.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This will display the user's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By default, the system has some
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,built-in sharing options, like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,messages, mail and notes; but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,other options will populate here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,from apps that have implemented
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a share extension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When creating the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,UIActivityViewController, you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,can parse in pretty much any
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,object, like a string, image or
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,URL.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But the best way to share the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,content of Your App is to use
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the universal link.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A universal link looks like a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,URL, but instead launches Your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,App.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At this stage, you might be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,asking, "Why share a URL?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a Web page."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to consider the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,person receiving the shared
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They may not have Your App
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,installed; so when tapping a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,universal link when Your App is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,not installed, it will fall back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to Safari, making it possible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for people with Your App to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,share content with new people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that do not need Your App to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,view the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if a new user receives a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,link to the content in Your App,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,an app banner can be displayed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in Safari, and it's a great way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase awareness of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,innovative experience to draw
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,new users of Your App.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Another way you can increase the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing experience for the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,recipient is to use Mockup in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Open Graph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the content shared in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,iMessage can be displayed in a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,rich format; so instead of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,looking like this, it can look
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,like this -- with an image
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,preview and title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The recipient of this message is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,much more likely to tap and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,follow this link.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So in summary, think about the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,content and experiences in Your
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,App.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What will your user like to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,share; and when is the most
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,meaningful time to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they know enough about the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,content to want to share it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the action button to launch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing and consider the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,placement of that button for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,context.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Universal links will work with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,recipients that don't have Your
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,App, and app banners can guide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,them to Your App.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, mock up your Web page
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with Open Graph for rich sharing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in iMessage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For more information, see the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,resources section of this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, and feel free to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,share it!
